    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you, but some people say the \"predatory practices\" you mentioned are just standard competitive strategies that led to better products for consumers. if the gov starts breaking these up, wouldn't that just kill the efficiency and innovation that people actually like? feels like a huge risk to take just to fix a theoretical problem.",
